type == 'bfloat16' and yOut.dtype == 'bfloat16' and meanOut.dtype == 'float32' and rstdOut.dtype == 'float32' and xOut.dtype == 'bfloat16') or (x1.dtype == 'float32' and x2.dtype == 'float32' and gamma.dtype == 'float32' and beta.dtype == 'float32' and biasOptional.dtype == 'float32' and yOut.dtype == 'float32' and meanOut.dtype == 'float32' and rstdOut.dtype == 'float32' and xOut.dtype == 'float32')",
        "relation_params": [
          "x1",
          "x2",
          "gamma",
          "beta",
          "biasOptional",
          "yOut",
          "meanOut",
          "rstdOut",
          "xOut"
        ],
        "src_text": "<term>Atlas A2 训练系列产品/Atlas A2 推理系列产品</term>、<term>Atlas A3 训练系列产品/Atlas A3 推理系列产品</term>：\n    | x1数据类型 | x2数据类型 | gamma数据类型 | beta数据类型 | biasOptional数据类型 | yOut数据类型 | meanOut数据类型 | rstdOut数据类型 | xOut数据类型 |\n    | -------- | -------- | ------------- | ------------- | ----------- | --------- | --------- | --------- | :-------- |\n    | FLOAT32  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  |\n    | FLOAT32  | BFLOAT16 | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  |\n    | FLOAT16  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  |\n    | BFLOAT16 | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  |\n    | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT16  |\n    | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | BFLOAT16 |\n    | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT16  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT16  |\n    | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | BFLOAT16 | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | BFLOAT16 |\n    | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  | FLOAT32  |"
